    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Trim, then chop your <strong>green beans </strong>in half</p><p>Roll your <strong>lime[s]</strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p>",
