      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mussels are cooked, add your <strong>sambal oelek</strong> and a squeeze of <strong>lime juice</strong> and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>sambal mussels</strong></p><p>Cut the remaining <strong>lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Tip: Discard any mussels which shells have not opened!</p>",
